snippet.title: Kingdom: New Lands - Skull Island FREE DLC! Out Now
snippet.description:
Kingdom: New Lands just got FREE DLC called Skull Island. It adds a tough new 6th island and is available now on Steam and Nintendo Switch.

Out soon for Xbox One, iOS, Android, and next year for PlayStation 4. 

http://store.steampowered.com/app/760200/Kingdom_New_Lands__Skull_Island/?snr=1_5_1100__1100
